sec.p: Analysis of the ROEO was performed using an Agilent 5975B mass spectrometer coupled to an Agilent 6890Â N gas chromatograph using the protocol previously described by Boukhris et al. [ 29]. The identification of the ROEO compounds was realized using a comparison of their retention times to n-alkanes, and their similarities to MS corresponding database (Wiley and NIST Library) and published data and spectra of authentic compounds.
